text: The Volkswagen Eos is a car produced by Volkswagen from 2006 to 2016. It replaced in 2001 the discontinued Volkswagen Golf Cabriolet it was Discontinued due to weak sales in 2016. == Engines == * 1.4 TSI 90 kW (122 hp) and 118 kW (160 hp) * 1.6 FSI 85 kW (115 hp) * 2.0 TSI 147 kW (200 hp) and 155 kW (210 hp) * 3.2 FSI 184 kW (250 hp) * 3.6 FSI 191 kW (260 hp) * 2.0 TDI 103 kW (140 hp) Eos Category:Front wheel drive vehicles Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles
title: Volkswagen Eos
